short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Automatically download PDFs into a user-defined path. For use only by existing customers who purchased Ecobillz Digitization module.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This plugin is part of Ecobillz Digitization SaaS platform. It is intended for use by Ecobillz customers who have purchased a valid license for its digitization platform. If you have not purchased Ecobillz digitization product please do not use this plugin/extension. Making a copy of this extension and/or reverse engineering this extension is strictly prohibited.
